      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality find. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine state, smelling and looking like new. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and no signs of wear. Buyers can expect a vehicle that drives as smoothly as the day it left the factory, offering a rare opportunity to own a top-tier example of this model.",
